tabletop (0.5) stable; urgency=low

  * Added game journal.
  * Added Dungeon Master notes to maps.
  * Support for links via chat.
  * Calculate distance between two points.
  * Small bugfixes and improvements.

 -- Hugo Leisink <hugo@leisink.net>  Sun, 14 Feb 2020 11:28:31 +0100

